subject: Basketball
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Terrence Williams had 24 points, 16 rebounds and 8 assists as 20th-ranked Louisville wore down Luke Harangody and No. 12 Notre Dame in an 87-73 overtime victory Monday night.
